(n+2)! = (n+2)(n+1)! = n(n+1)! + 2(n+1)!
(n + 1)! - n! = n(n!) 
n > 1
\color{blue}{(n+2)!} -\color{red}{(n+1)!} = (n+1)(n+1)!
\color{blue}{(n+2)!} -\color{red}{(n+1)!} =\color{blue}{(n+2)}(n+1)! - \color{red}{(n+1)}(n!)
=\color{blue}{n}(n+1)! + \color{green}{2}(n+1)! - \color{red}{n}(n!) -\color{red}{1}(n!) 
